title: Path Painter
description:
How to Play Path Painter:
- Click and drag (or tap and drag) starting from a numbered cell.
- The number indicates the exact length the path must be (including the start cell).
- Draw a continuous path by moving to adjacent (up, down, left, right) empty cells.
Paths cannot cross themselves or other paths.
- You cannot draw over other numbers.
- Fill the entire grid with paths of the correct lengths to win!
- Clicking on a completed path allows you to clear and redraw it.
